{"tid":2171752,"cid":21,"subCid":8,"title":"口琴撚請進","createTime":"2020-08-24T07:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T20:52:25.000Z","uid":366574,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"798377a236ff5482f45f410aa97b6169f8d4d73a","tid":2171752,"uid":366574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:16:40.000Z","msg":"小弟冇咩音樂天份<br />\n但覺得口琴細細個,好似幾好玩<br />\n想請問一下有玩口琴既巴絲<br />\n初學者要買咩牌子同咩model<br />\n同埋有冇話一開始學吹咩歌好練D?"},{"pid":"c0664e5922a0952980cd029461430bcdc0a485e3","tid":2171752,"uid":118217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:24:59.000Z","msg":"學嘢"},{"pid":"3d33f7f92e8ec73f22084e1e623be652df853a2e","tid":2171752,"uid":128364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:45:57.000Z","msg":"我都想知 之前係學校報左免費<br />\n比個肺炎搞到取消左<br />\n好想學"},{"pid":"59b32169830f0f34bb1617f592dc3e8106577c2a","tid":2171752,"uid":55056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:59:55.000Z","msg":"首先口琴基本分三種，藍調，複音同半音階<br />\n<br />\n你揀左隻先，因為大家技巧唔共通，通常只會練一種"},{"pid":"d0c839bb9eae0e8feb043915adc113ae8009e1fe","tid":2171752,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T08:02:25.000Z","msg":"A wavy line in front of a chord means to plqy the notes quickly in order rather than simultaneously; to give a chord a harp-like effect. A rolled chord is a type of broken chord. It is a chord whose noted are played one after another beginning at the bottom. Use second and fourth fingers on all broken thirds in the right hand and fourth, third, second and first fingers on F sharp, G, G sharp and A in the left hand."},{"pid":"3134ea8d0455fe7734f9acfdae7715a7458e5762","tid":2171752,"uid":80164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T08:02:42.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢<br />\n細個已經有興趣，但屋企人話會吹到變孖潤腸一直唔比我學<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7f2b74ae1bc4a5dd0616782438101155be9761","tid":2171752,"uid":366574,"l